@startuml Governance_Process

!theme plain
title Development Governance Process

|Developer|
start
:Receive feature request;

:Check if it affects business logic;

if (Affects logic?) then (yes)
  |PlantUML|
  :Open relevant .puml diagram;
  :Add/modify rules with IDs;
  :Commit diagram changes;
  
  |Developer|
  :Implement code matching diagram;
else (no)
  :Implement directly;
endif

|Developer|
:Run lint + typecheck;
:Create PR;

|Reviewer|
:Check diagram matches code;
:Verify rule IDs exist;
:Approve or request changes;

|Developer|
:Merge to main;
stop

note right
  **Key Checkpoints:**
  - Diagram updated before code
  - Rule IDs are unique
  - Enforcement mechanism documented
  - Migration file if DB changes
end note

@enduml
